descriptor.name: Noise ColorFit Caliber Smartwatch - Partner Exclusive
descriptor.short_desc: The Noise ColorFit Caliber smartwatch features a 1.69 TFT LCD display so that you can enjoy clear & sharp visuals. 60 sports modes give you the freedom to work out to the routine of your choice. With Noise Health Suite, manage your daily health with a series of health monitoring tools such as the SpO2 monitor, HR monitor, sleep monitor & stress monitor. ColorFit Caliber also comes with a Body temperature sensor to track your fluctuating body temperature. Up to 15 days of battery helps you keep up with your busy lifestyle. An IP68 water resistance rating ensures that your smartwatch is protected from splashes, sweat and rain. This smartwatch for men and women lets you express yourself with 100+ animated, cloud-based & customisable watch faces. The preset quick replies feature for Android helps you stay connected and live hands-free. Additional features such as weather forecasts, customisable reminders, remote music control, call rejection and a lot more, enable you to live a connected life.
